 PS5 独占<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/final-fantasy-xvi-review-ps5-140058789.html"><em>《XVI》</em>所</a>遗漏的粉丝。这也是一种接触日本游戏玩家和日式角色扮演游戏爱好者的尝试。 Xbox <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.tweaktown.com/news/91834/phil-spencer-explains-why-japanese-games-skip-xbox/index.html">在日本举步维艰</a>，很大程度上是因为当地工作室跳过该平台，转而使用任天堂和索尼的国产游戏机。这款游戏不会突然改善微软的命运，但它确实消除了一些玩家采用的障碍。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/final-fantasy-xiv-comes-to-xbox-next-spring-192903645.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/final-fantasy-xiv-comes-to-xbox-next-spring-192903645.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 3a1aef13-2025-4a1e-875b-689313ea8d5f</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jul 2023 19:29:03 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690572544</ingested><modified> 2023-07-28T19:29:09+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Game Consoles]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/a2d3f7b0-2d78-11ee-afef-a860b4af18f6" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/a2d3f7b0-2d78-11ee-afef-a860b4af18f6" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifie